(
function setThemeMode() {
	if (typeof(Storage) !== "undefined") {
		if(localStorage.getItem("darkMode") == 1){
			document.body.classList.add("dark-mode");
		}
	}
	
})();	
</script>

	<script>
(
function setThemeMode() {
	if (typeof(Storage) !== "undefined") {
		if(localStorage.getItem("darkMode") == 1){
			document.body.classList.add("dark-mode");
		}
	}
	
})();	
</script>

	<script>
(
function setThemeMode() {
	if (typeof(Storage) !== "undefined") {
		if(localStorage.getItem("darkMode") == 1){
			document.body.classList.add("dark-mode");
		}
	}
	
})();	
</script>
